  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he did this from out of his apartment where he was living near-- he still had a-- he was still seeing some, some private-- he was still conducting a private practice.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He had this opportunity.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it's very unfortunate that he-- that he didn't do it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He could have left that anywhere-- Jews could leave Germany, I think, up until-- not too many problems up until 1938, the night when the Crystal Night, which is now, you know, known as the official, you know, start of the Holocaust really, in a way.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because that's when they smashed the Jewish doors, and burned synagogues, and, and also killed some of the Jewish people in Germany.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By SS-- by-- no, by the Storm Troopers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was not the SS.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was the S-- the, the Schutzstaffel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, he had a--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He had a completely [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] non-caring attitude about the situation because he felt he was a German first.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He had been a major in World War I in charge of a German military field hospital in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because, if you remember, in World War I, Germany, Austria, and Hungary were all united allies against Russia, Britain, France, and later on, against the US.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so he-- you know, on his-- in his apartment was a-- was a picture of him in full German officer's uniform with all the decorations.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he felt very strongly about being a German.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when-- and I, I, I, I don't-- I, I, I didn't witness those things, those discussions that my father and my-- had with my mother, and her brother, my uncle, who was a pacifist, who had-- who had been a contentious objector to the draft and World War I.",
      "word_count": 50
    }
  ],
